name: THE REWIND BUTTON
description:
This has been my logo pretty much as long as I have had a music career.

Its a K for Kane.. but also its a rewind button because my lyrics have a lot in them and you may need to rewind to catch everything. 

Who am i kidding... you will DEF have to rewind... im awesome lol

All that humility i just served you aside, this is a great way to support what I do. 

Going to leave the price at 2 Tez, that way if you ever want to be nice you can pick one up

I plan on doing something fun with these for people who have a few. So if you have 10 or 20 of em, they will be swapped out for something awesome down the road.

Till then...

peace out
